{"tid":1086943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【先知】撤資定為交棒？李嘉誠賣走中港2,000億資產","createTime":"2019-04-01T05:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T06:20:50.000Z","uid":50457,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ee521970c855ddf0c9ed35153f25a7ee80539dce","tid":1086943,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:22:52.000Z","msg":"長和（001）主席李嘉誠近年屢被批評中港兩地「撤資」，事件緣由可追溯至2012年時唐英年、梁振英競逐特首，撐唐的李嘉誠長子、長和聯席董事總經理李澤鉅公然批評香港政治不穩，「倒不如赴外地投資」。據本報統計，長和系2013年起至今，出售中港資產規模近2,000億元。亦有意見認為李嘉誠賣資產、合併重組、遷冊舉動，實際是鋪路兒子接棒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180317/57957224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180317%2F57957224&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=2b4861b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180317%2F57957224&h=813c85df\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180317/57957224</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">實際是逃出修改刑事條例</span><br />\n其他地產商，所有資產已落入中共口中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果未來幾大地產商都遷刪，證明香港徹底玩完"},{"pid":"1a9f960f2a9d8675281e7e025dc27b25008bf856","tid":1086943,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:27:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0beb23f4ba82afd3de9397bfac6e299a2ac17569","tid":1086943,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:28:35.000Z","msg":"相信係有預謀做冧大陸經濟，擾亂市場秩序。"},{"pid":"0a3c45d3fb14f